data.description: This impressive property offers a generous floor plan with 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. Enhanced by two spacious living areas, its layout offers flexibility for casual living or sophisticated entertaining Inside, the home boasts a mix of modern and timeless interior details, offering a perfect canvas to bring in your personal style. Outdoors, the elegant brick exterior adds a touch of classic charm. Don't miss this opportunity to own a slice of Texas suburbia!
